Interface View

public interface View extends com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.Named
A view is a named repository of MapDrawable objects which can be updated.

    name

  • Method Details

    • add

      void add​(MapDrawable drawable)
      Adds the given object to the view. Since it is not identified, it can never be removed or updated.

    • clear

      void clear()
      Clears the set of MapDrawable objects held by this view. Not all views necessarily support this operation. If the view does not support the operation, calling this method will have no effect.
